<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1173 Agu 
<lb n="2"/>nēṁṭi virōdhikrutsaṁvatsara kārttikaparvva 
<lb n="3"/>nimityamuna śrītripurāṁttakadēvaraku 
<lb n="4"/><unclear>me</unclear>ḍapīkil<unclear>la</unclear> nūkiseṭi tammuḍu Eṟṟanūki 
<lb n="5"/>seṭi tama ta<unclear>ṁ</unclear>ḍri jāmiseṭikiṁ tama talli māra 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>sānikiṁ dharmuvugānu Akhaṁḍadīpamu 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>naku pe<unclear>ḍi</unclear>na mōdālu 25 vīniṁ cēkoni Evu 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ramu Eṟebōyuḍu nitya māneṁḍu neyi 
<lb n="9"/>tana putrānupavitrikaramu Ācaṁdrārka 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>mugā naḍapaṁgalavāḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
